race.comment: ANOTHER JIMMY (3) was game in defeat at the latest run, finishing second and beaten 1.75 lengths (22.45) behind Elite Deluxe at this track. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Makes plenty of appeal. SUNSET OYSTER (5) was an impressive last start winner, scoring an excellent 22.24 win and a new Best time this course and distance. This tougher but looks a leading chance again. MAJORA'S MASK (1) turned spotting a big start finishing seventh (30.74) last time in a Grade 5/6 at Northam. Form at the trip sound including three wins. Shapes as one to consider. GO GETTEM TILLY (8) missed the placings here most recently but can sneak into the finish with the right run.
